\s Zamani mjini mwa Yerusalemu
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Zamani mjini mwa Yerusalemu waisrael’ waliabudu. \bd*\bd Wakristo\bd*\bd  wa sasa wanakusanyika kuomba, kusifu \bd*\bd Mwokozi\bd*\bd . \bd*
